**Buy-back Final Notification Summary**  
- **Type:** On-market buy-back  
- **Total shares bought back:** 43,173,531 (10% of issued shares)  
- **Total consideration paid:** AUD 17,668,470.29  
- **Price range:** AUD 0.320 (low) to AUD 0.495 (high)  
- **Buy-back period:** 27/11/2024 to 26/11/2025 (completed early)  
- **Broker:** Goldman Sachs  
- **No shareholder approval required.**  

*Key impact:* Reduction in shares outstanding (liquidity decrease) and capital return to shareholders.
